Pinstripe Limo by Lauren Thompson (free for personal use only/commercial use requires a donation):  
 [http://www.nymfont.com/2009/06/fonts.html](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317171404/http:/www.nymfont.com/2009/06/fonts.html "http://www.nymfont.com/2009/06/fonts.html")

A commercial font call Trend Sans 5 is also very close, though a bit wider:  
 [http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/latinotype/trend/](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317171404/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/latinotype/trend/ "http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/latinotype/trend/")
